<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمِلْكِ الْمُشْتَرَكِ وَالْحَقِّ الْمُشْتَرَكِ إِلاَّ بِرِضَا الشُّرَكَاءِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَتَفْصِيل ذَلِكَ يُنْظَرُ فِي:</span> <span class="c2">(مِيَاهٌ، نَهْرٌ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
